  "short_description": "Navigate the Math Castle and Maze solving addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, and number matching to earn Stars unlocking Characters and Mini-Games: 3 in a row Tic-tac-toe, Memory card match, timed jumping in Spire Run, and Dance Party patterns. Come play again to beat your high score!",
