  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/4e7e8a61feb2bf9e95eb908300a71fef.apng?t=1765341494\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/4e7e8a61feb2bf9e95eb908300a71fef.poster.avif?t=1765341494\" class=\"bb_img\" width=610 height=250 /></picture></span>Embark on a mathematical journey through our enchanting castle filled with engaging challenges and delightful surprises. K-5 children can practice their number and math skills in various ways, matching words with the numbers, addition, and subtraction, with the option to turn on multiplication and division, or even extend the number range far above and below the starting 0 to 10. Go down the random path to get a mix of question types for a more advanced challenge. Solve your way through the Math Magical Maze. Stars reset each day, so come push yourself to make a new high score. Older children and adults can come for the brain teasers with fun breaks in the mini-game arcade.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c1b14846b54f0ce4895d580785bb93fa.poster.avif?t=1765341494\" width=600 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c1b14846b54f0ce4895d580785bb93fa.webm?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c1b14846b54f0ce4895d580785bb93fa.mp4?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Practice Math Skills</strong>: Navigate through various math rooms, dodge spikes, and earn Stars by answering questions correctly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c4e3d55ef2657ce56fef3397407335a1.poster.avif?t=1765341494\" aria-label=\"Owley, the blue owl, traveling a maze to solve math problems.\" width=600 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c4e3d55ef2657ce56fef3397407335a1.webm?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c4e3d55ef2657ce56fef3397407335a1.mp4?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Mini-Games: </strong>Memory Match starts with 4 cards and adds more cards up to 18 as you keep clearing the board. Spire Run gets faster and harder the longer you go. Remember more moves as the Simon-style Dance Party goes on longer. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tailor Your Challenge</strong>: Start with Addition, Subtraction, and Word Match. When you’re ready, turn on Multiplication and Division. Even turn on Time to practice reading analog clocks. Mix things up with the Random room, or Math Magical Maze, which will give you any of your selected math modes. Set your number range anywhere from -9999 to 9999. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/6b36832e72af4399105f0141a0781e94.poster.avif?t=1765341494\" aria-label=\"Oozzee triggering a room with a large clock. \" width=592 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/6b36832e72af4399105f0141a0781e94.webm?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/6b36832e72af4399105f0141a0781e94.mp4?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Content</strong>: Discover <span class=\"bb_strike\">8</span> now 9! charming skins and conquer 4 captivating mini-games: Memory, Tic-Tac-Toe, Dance Party, and Spire Run. <br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rewarding System</strong>: Spend Stars to unlock exciting new skins and mini-games, or keep hold of them to push up your daily high score. Check in each day to beat your high scores for Stars and each mini-game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/1c6d6221e8f29f2534ab23999b4eb2a0.poster.avif?t=1765341494\" width=620 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/1c6d6221e8f29f2534ab23999b4eb2a0.webm?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/1c6d6221e8f29f2534ab23999b4eb2a0.mp4?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intuitive Controls</strong>: Enjoy seamless game-play with touchscreen, mouse, or keyboard inputs, including support for controllers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Pixel Art</strong>: Immerse yourself in the game's enchanting world, crafted with love in Aseprite.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Developers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphics and Game Design - Nicole Haynie</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original Sound Track - Silly Little Muse sillylittlemuse on Linktree</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound Effects - Wesley Barros @wbaudio on X</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/4e7e8a61feb2bf9e95eb908300a71fef.apng?t=1765341494\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/4e7e8a61feb2bf9e95eb908300a71fef.poster.avif?t=1765341494\" class=\"bb_img\" width=610 height=250 /></picture></span>Embark on a mathematical journey through our enchanting castle filled with engaging challenges and delightful surprises. K-5 children can practice their number and math skills in various ways, matching words with the numbers, addition, and subtraction, with the option to turn on multiplication and division, or even extend the number range far above and below the starting 0 to 10. Go down the random path to get a mix of question types for a more advanced challenge. Solve your way through the Math Magical Maze. Stars reset each day, so come push yourself to make a new high score. Older children and adults can come for the brain teasers with fun breaks in the mini-game arcade.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c1b14846b54f0ce4895d580785bb93fa.poster.avif?t=1765341494\" width=600 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c1b14846b54f0ce4895d580785bb93fa.webm?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860170/extras/c1b14846b54f0ce4895d580785bb93fa.mp4?t=1765341494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Practice Math Skills</strong>: Navigate through various math rooms, dodge spikes, and earn Stars by answering questions c